---
const appName = "台股ETF";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
        <title>{appName} — 主動式 ETF 換股雷達</title>
        <meta name="description" content="每個交易日自動比對主動式 ETF 持股，新進、剔除、加減碼一目了然。折溢價總覽、即時報價、配息日曆。" />
        <meta property="og:title" content={`${appName} — 主動式 ETF 換股雷達`} />
        <meta property="og:description" content="每個交易日自動比對主動式 ETF 持股，新進、剔除、加減碼一目了然。" />
        <meta property="og:url" content="https://twetf.dearhui.com" />
        <link rel="sitemap" href="/sitemap-index.xml" />
        <style>
            @import "../styles/global.css";
        </style>
    </head>
    <body class="min-h-screen bg-white text-gray-900">
        <!-- Nav -->
        <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-gray-200/60 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl">
            <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-5xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
                <a href="/" class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 no-underline">
                    {appName}
                </a>
                <span class="rounded-full bg-teal-50 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-teal-700">
                    即將上架
                </span>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <!-- Hero -->
        <section class="overflow-hidden px-6 pb-16 pt-20 sm:pb-24 sm:pt-28">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
                    主動式 ETF<br /><span class="text-teal-600">換股雷達</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-lg text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
                    每個交易日自動比對主動式 ETF 持股快照——新進場、出場、加減碼，一目了然。
                </p>
                <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gray-900 px-7 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg">
                        <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.8-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/>
                        </svg>
                        即將上架 App Store
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">iOS 18 以上・公開資料永遠免費</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Features -->
        <section class="bg-gray-50 px-6 py-24 sm:py-32">
            <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
                <div class="animate-on-scroll rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-100 text-2xl">🛰️</div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">換股雷達</h2>
                    <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
                        全台主動式 ETF 持股異動每日更新，新進、剔除、加減碼分類呈現，申贖造成的等比縮放已校正——看到的都是真換股。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="animate-on-scroll rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-100 text-2xl">💹</div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">折溢價總覽</h2>
                    <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
                        380+ 檔上市櫃 ETF 收盤價與折溢價一次看，主動式／被動式篩選、折溢價排序，抓出溢價過熱的標的。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="animate-on-scroll rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-100 text-2xl">⭐</div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">自選與桌面 Widget</h2>
                    <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
                        自選清單盤中即時報價、iCloud 跨裝置同步；桌面 Widget 一眼掌握自選折溢價，不用開 App。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="animate-on-scroll rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-100 text-2xl">📅</div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">配息日曆</h2>
                    <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
                        除息日、發放日、每單位配息與殖利率整理成日曆，領息節奏一目了然。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="border-t border-gray-200">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-8 text-center text-sm text-gray-400">
                <div class="mb-3 flex justify-center gap-6">
                    <a href="/privacy" class="transition hover:text-gray-600">隱私權政策</a>
                </div>
                <p class="mx-auto mb-3 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
                    本網站與 App 提供之資訊僅供參考，不構成投資建議。投資一定有風險，申購前應詳閱公開說明書。
                </p>
                <p>&copy; {year} dearhui studio</p>
                <p class="mt-1">
                    <a href="mailto:dearhui.studio@gmail.com" class="transition hover:text-gray-600">
                        dearhui.studio@gmail.com
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </footer>

        <script>
            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
                entries.forEach((e) => {
                    if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add("visible");
                });
            }, { threshold: 0.1 });
            document.querySelectorAll(".animate-on-scroll").forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
        </script>
    </body>
</html>
